        <head>
          <emph>Related Material</emph>
        </head>
        <p>Since the papers of the den Bleyker family and Nathaniel Aldrich Balch and family were received from the same donor, there were many instances in which portions of one collection were mixed with the other. Anyone interested in either den Bleyker or Balch would no doubt find it worthwhile to look at both collections, since the relationship of these individuals to each other was close.</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
